Wave optics and ray tracing library for Python

Author: Kaan Ak≈üit
Licence: GPLV2

Dependency: matplotlib, pygame, numpy

Currently available methods inside source/lib/odak.py

- Method for Fresnel and Fraunhofer diffractions
- Method for creating apertures such as circular, rectangular, slits, sinusoidal amplitude grating, lens and two slits
- Method for plotting crossection, 2D & 3D data
- Method for diverging and converging spherical wave
- Method for diverging and converging gaussian beam
